{"tid":415893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[插針遍天下]青衣長青邨擬建4座40層高插針公屋","createTime":"2017-09-27T10:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:16:56.000Z","uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20ccd877ddef649b72e80f1994a7fb6badaddb2e","tid":415893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ktrhk/photos/1855454057798892/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fktrhk%2Fphotos%2F1855454057798892%2F&d=MPVPbIJfcNROW%2BQtm8S5TWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=74eada44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ktrhk/photos/1855454057798892/</a><br />\n<br />\n突發消息<br />\n長青邨擬建4座40層高插針式公屋大廈<br />\n<br />\n地盤範圍包括現有長青巴士總站、長青社區中心、前張熾昌小學、青松樓對出停車場及球場、青桃樓旁籃球場。<br />\n<br />\n房屋署建議於上址興建4幢約40層高公營住宅樓宇，約提供3,050個單位，新增人口約8,550人，預計於2018年起分三期動工，料於2028年全數落成。<br />\n<br />\n區議會房屋事務委員會將於10月3日的會議上討論上述計劃，本組織將會繼續關注事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n緊貼社區消息，請即加入Telegram group:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ktrhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fktrhk&d=MPVPbIJfcNROW%2BQtm8S5TWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=dd13ea7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ktrhk</a><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n1.區議會文件 22/D/2017<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kwt/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/HAC/12173/22_D_2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkwt%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2FHAC%2F12173%2F22_D_2017.pdf&d=MPVPbIJfcNROW%2BQtm8S5TWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8dd3611c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kwt/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/HAC/12173/22_D_2017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2.蘋果日報報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170926&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57259276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170926%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57259276&d=MPVPbIJfcNROW%2BQtm8S5TWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3a597136\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170926%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57259276&h=926c4b66\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170926&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57259276</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ebf2dbbf869a38d008e54d519ec4d987b0d7a735","tid":415893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b3e83b4f005bbeea8ebb6d02901dadbf1da989","tid":415893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b166b81790af7a854d29b5a84e728355c9bbad","tid":415893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39bff141ea2324c9fb0b087d27a474e5b0d4914","tid":415893,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"咁都唔順手重建長青邨真係屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbe9279eec60d5f2359e9833d1d266aa14b8a89","tid":415893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都唔順手重建長青邨真係屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有大把屋邨舊過長青<br />\n房署而家除咗白田邨之外，其他舊邨都唔願重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}